1
00:00:31,834 --> 00:00:35,544
[Shishimaru Joins the Fight]

2
00:00:46,099 --> 00:00:48,384
Kenichi, wait for me

3
00:00:51,731 --> 00:00:52,904
Zero again?

4
00:00:53,123 --> 00:00:54,736
You're not loyal enough for a day!

5
00:00:54,786 --> 00:00:56,523
If you were willing to let me peek, this wouldn't happen

6
00:00:56,574 --> 00:00:57,795
How can you cheat?

7
00:00:57,845 --> 00:00:59,096
If you don't want a zero

8
00:00:59,161 --> 00:01:00,622
then study harder!

9
00:01:00,647 --> 00:01:02,632
Ah, you sound just like Mommy

10
00:01:07,821 --> 00:01:08,705
I'm so scared!

11
00:01:08,730 --> 00:01:10,469
Oh, calm down, no need to be scared

12
00:01:10,519 --> 00:01:12,093
This dog is on a leash

13
00:01:12,144 --> 00:01:13,589
Huh, what are you going to do about it?

14
00:01:21,343 --> 00:01:24,072
Oh no, it's not on a leash anymore

15
00:01:24,122 --> 00:01:26,295
Kenichi, you're a big strong man

16
00:01:26,335 --> 00:01:28,248
- What are you afraid of?
- Save me!

17
00:01:52,424 --> 00:01:53,454
Wow, that's amazing

18
00:01:53,505 --> 00:01:54,429
Awesome!

19
00:01:54,480 --> 00:01:56,444
Kenichi, you're acting tough

20
00:01:56,494 --> 00:01:58,134
This puppy...

21
00:01:58,184 --> 00:01:59,787
You are truly amazing!

22
00:01:59,814 --> 00:02:00,837
Ah, what a waste of time

23
00:02:00,887 --> 00:02:03,360
That puppy won't talk to you anyway

24
00:02:04,664 --> 00:02:05,872
Wait a moment!

25
00:02:09,398 --> 00:02:10,898
It's gone?

26
00:02:12,205 --> 00:02:14,305
I don't know where it ran off to

27
00:02:19,714 --> 00:02:21,384
It looks kinda like that

28
00:02:21,814 --> 00:02:24,043
The dog you drew doesn't even look like a dog

29
00:02:24,094 --> 00:02:25,872
Hey, don't criticize me

30
00:02:25,923 --> 00:02:28,744
That's right, I remember it had something on its forehead like a...

31
00:02:28,864 --> 00:02:30,620
A shuriken

32
00:02:32,144 --> 00:02:33,877
Oh, could it be…

33
00:02:35,916 --> 00:02:38,090
But that's impossible

34
00:02:38,637 --> 00:02:40,544
Hattori-kun, so you've seen him?

35
00:02:41,334 --> 00:02:42,945
Oh no, no, I haven't

36
00:02:42,995 --> 00:02:44,824
But I will try my best to help you find him

37
00:02:44,948 --> 00:02:46,704
Uh… excuse me

38
00:02:50,921 --> 00:02:52,873
Seems like Shishimaru has really come

39
00:02:52,924 --> 00:02:54,352
I originally left him back at my village

40
00:02:54,403 --> 00:02:55,784
I really didn't expect him

41
00:02:57,176 --> 00:02:59,104
Yan…

42
00:03:14,367 --> 00:03:16,400
Oh, I don't need to look for Shishimaru.

43
00:03:16,451 --> 00:03:18,491
I just need to use food to lure him in.

44
00:03:36,727 --> 00:03:38,184
Ah, Shishimaru.

45
00:03:38,527 --> 00:03:40,076
Who told you to come here?

46
00:03:40,127 --> 00:03:42,300
So outrageous, go back to the village!

47
00:03:43,674 --> 00:03:46,007
You know, I'm not in Tokyo for fun

48
00:03:46,064 --> 00:03:47,621
I'm here to learn.

49
00:03:55,811 --> 00:03:59,347
Oh? It's a ninja technique, the bone-dissecting, shrinking, escaping net method.

50
00:03:59,397 --> 00:04:01,531
I didn't expect your technique to improve so much.

51
00:04:01,926 --> 00:04:02,966
Excuse me...

52
00:04:03,383 --> 00:04:05,123
But you can't stay here.

53
00:04:05,173 --> 00:04:07,586
You will affect Kenichi's family life.

54
00:04:14,065 --> 00:04:17,116
Well... Okay, I'll let you stay here.

55
00:04:17,167 --> 00:04:19,894
Tomorrow, no matter what, you have to go back to the village, understand?

56
00:04:33,089 --> 00:04:34,494
Oh my, who is it?

57
00:04:34,534 --> 00:04:36,784
Who on earth ate all my rice?

58
00:04:36,835 --> 00:04:37,745
What's wrong?

59
00:04:37,794 --> 00:04:38,904
What's going on?

60
00:04:39,634 --> 00:04:42,635
I cooked a big pot of rice, why is it all gone?

61
00:04:42,686 --> 00:04:44,145
- I don't know.
- I don't know.

62
00:04:46,739 --> 00:04:48,692
No need to ask, it must be Shishimaru

63
00:04:50,411 --> 00:04:51,659
Oh no, Shishimaru

64
00:04:55,414 --> 00:04:57,984
Oh, where did the dog come from? Is it from Hattori-kun?

65
00:04:58,035 --> 00:04:59,733
Yes, I'm so sorry

66
00:04:59,784 --> 00:05:01,880
Tomorrow I will definitely send it back to the village

67
00:05:01,931 --> 00:05:03,220
Oh, wait

68
00:05:03,261 --> 00:05:05,511
I recognize this dog, it's my savior!

69
00:05:05,561 --> 00:05:06,987
Please don't make him go

70
00:05:07,038 --> 00:05:08,651
Let's let him stay here

71
00:05:08,702 --> 00:05:10,794
But Shishimaru is greedy and rude

72
00:05:10,844 --> 00:05:13,223
He'll cause you a lot of trouble.

73
00:05:18,569 --> 00:05:20,125
This dog is so clever.

74
00:05:20,176 --> 00:05:22,544
Why don't we keep him? Okay, Mom?

75
00:05:23,216 --> 00:05:24,584
But I'm afraid...

76
00:05:32,988 --> 00:05:35,950
Although he is very greedy, he is really very clever.

77
00:05:36,001 --> 00:05:37,353
Okay, let's keep him.

78
00:05:37,404 --> 00:05:39,827
Tomorrow, we'll build him a doghouse, okay?

79
00:05:39,878 --> 00:05:41,917
Hooray!

80
00:05:43,357 --> 00:05:46,557
They're so nice to you, why don't you thank them?

81
00:05:55,933 --> 00:05:58,947
After a couple compliments he's already beside himself with joy.

82
00:05:59,341 --> 00:06:01,885
He's lovely, my parents have decided to take him in.

83
00:06:01,935 --> 00:06:02,624
Really?

84
00:06:02,674 --> 00:06:04,351
I actually liked him a lot too.

85
00:06:04,401 --> 00:06:07,504
But he's Hattori-kun's friend, don't break them up.

86
00:06:08,760 --> 00:06:10,760
Ah, what's that sound?

87
00:06:12,348 --> 00:06:15,018
That snore is so loud the whole street can hear it.

88
00:06:15,059 --> 00:06:16,620
Hey, Shishimaru, please

89
00:06:16,671 --> 00:06:18,936
Shishimaru, this bed is for me to sleep in.

90
00:06:19,265 --> 00:06:21,609
Having Shishimaru around is really troublesome.

91
00:06:29,931 --> 00:06:32,944
[The Goal is Full Points]

92
00:06:38,000 --> 00:06:39,537
Okay, the test is tomorrow

93
00:06:39,593 --> 00:06:41,019
Oh no, another test

94
00:06:41,070 --> 00:06:43,356
Don't be noisy... hurry up and get in order

95
00:06:43,407 --> 00:06:44,534
You don't need to be nervous

96
00:06:44,584 --> 00:06:47,120
Reviewing homework as usual is enough

97
00:06:47,170 --> 00:06:47,994
Yes!

98
00:06:48,384 --> 00:06:49,500
People who get zero on the exam

99
00:06:49,550 --> 00:06:50,894
answer particularly loudly

100
00:06:52,862 --> 00:06:55,397
Oh no, as long as I work hard, I will definitely pass

101
00:06:55,448 --> 00:06:58,310
As long as I pass, no one will laugh at me, okay!

102
00:07:02,344 --> 00:07:03,424
I'm back!

103
00:07:07,256 --> 00:07:08,424
Yan...

104
00:07:10,677 --> 00:07:11,941
What's wrong with Kenichi today?

105
00:07:11,997 --> 00:07:13,672
He didn't even glance at the afternoon snacks.

106
00:07:13,723 --> 00:07:16,204
How about I take them to him? Here.

107
00:07:16,614 --> 00:07:18,384
Yan...

108
00:07:19,050 --> 00:07:21,424
Hey, Kenichi, open the door!

109
00:07:23,158 --> 00:07:25,162
You're not eating such delicious snacks?

110
00:07:25,212 --> 00:07:26,925
Are you feeling sick?

111
00:07:30,173 --> 00:07:32,400
Is the goal to get full marks? Oh, I understand now.

112
00:07:32,445 --> 00:07:33,852
Your approach is very...

113
00:07:35,067 --> 00:07:36,878
I see you have so much determination

114
00:07:36,928 --> 00:07:39,400
I will help you achieve your wish, don't worry

115
00:07:39,451 --> 00:07:40,921
Hattori-kun, thank you so much

116
00:07:40,971 --> 00:07:43,624
Alright, I must get full marks tomorrow

117
00:07:43,841 --> 00:07:48,144
- Kenichi, come out and play ball
- Kenichi, come out and play ball

118
00:07:48,504 --> 00:07:49,702
Oh, hold on a moment

119
00:07:49,752 --> 00:07:51,262
Let me help push them away

120
00:07:51,312 --> 00:07:54,024
You should study hard, you can't play now

121
00:07:54,075 --> 00:07:57,495
It's not too late to study after I play

122
00:07:57,545 --> 00:07:58,996
Why are you acting like that?

123
00:07:59,825 --> 00:08:00,889
Just kidding.

124
00:08:00,939 --> 00:08:02,027
Oh, Shishimaru

125
00:08:02,052 --> 00:08:03,282
You don't believe me, do you?

126
00:08:03,332 --> 00:08:05,245
I really can do what I say I can do.

127
00:08:11,171 --> 00:08:13,694
Kenichi knows how to study hard, so exciting!

128
00:08:13,719 --> 00:08:16,448
Of course, I always got zero on tests and people laughed at me.

129
00:08:16,499 --> 00:08:19,393
Alright then, if you get good grades, I'll give you a prize.

130
00:08:19,434 --> 00:08:20,181
Really?

131
00:08:20,221 --> 00:08:22,221
Okay, tonight I'll study all the way until dawn.

132
00:08:22,272 --> 00:08:24,766
- Okay, I'm full.
- I'm full too.

133
00:08:28,774 --> 00:08:30,876
Oh, nice!

134
00:08:30,933 --> 00:08:33,263
- You just promised Mum you'd study.
- Oh, let me see for a moment.

135
00:08:33,307 --> 00:08:36,407
- You can't watch TV, yan...
- It doesn't matter

136
00:08:37,606 --> 00:08:40,356
Oh dear, the show will be over soon.

137
00:08:42,164 --> 00:08:44,297
A real man should be able to do it.

138
00:08:44,338 --> 00:08:46,424
A word once spoken can't be taken back.

139
00:08:47,152 --> 00:08:48,481
Even so

140
00:08:48,532 --> 00:08:50,522
What's the use of cramming at the last minute?

141
00:08:50,573 --> 00:08:52,299
The math is hard.

142
00:08:56,639 --> 00:08:58,193
Hey, don't go!

143
00:09:00,245 --> 00:09:01,062
Kenichi

144
00:09:01,103 --> 00:09:03,883
You must fully commit to study successfully

145
00:09:03,938 --> 00:09:06,464
 Ah... Got it...

146
00:09:14,967 --> 00:09:16,877
Maybe I'm too strict

147
00:09:16,918 --> 00:09:18,374
But I'm only doing it for your own good

148
00:09:18,434 --> 00:09:19,476
Ah, I understand

149
00:09:19,527 --> 00:09:22,528
But it shouldn't matter if I sleep a bit

150
00:09:23,440 --> 00:09:24,857
You can't! You should know

151
00:09:24,907 --> 00:09:26,650
you can't get full marks

152
00:09:26,700 --> 00:09:30,229
- You're so embarrassing, hurry up
- Oh, Hattori-kun

153
00:09:30,474 --> 00:09:32,891
I'm so hungry now, please.

154
00:09:32,941 --> 00:09:34,263
Oh right, if you're hungry

155
00:09:34,314 --> 00:09:35,360
you'll have no energy to study.

156
00:09:35,400 --> 00:09:37,120
Okay, I'll get you something to eat.

157
00:09:46,024 --> 00:09:47,250
So annoying!

158
00:09:48,284 --> 00:09:49,477
So annoying!

159
00:09:50,177 --> 00:09:53,437
Yan... Huh?

160
00:09:56,228 --> 00:09:57,656
Fire!

161
00:10:02,041 --> 00:10:04,384
Shishimaru, that's a bit much!

162
00:10:09,527 --> 00:10:11,818
I'm so tired from studying for so long.

163
00:10:11,868 --> 00:10:14,304
- Still not enough
- Yeah... huh?

164
00:10:14,634 --> 00:10:17,474
Oh, now it's a perfect score.

165
00:10:26,923 --> 00:10:30,009
- I just want...
- Kenichi... are you in the bathroom?

166
00:10:30,050 --> 00:10:31,277
Yes...

167
00:10:33,013 --> 00:10:35,347
Ah, fine. Since I can't sleep

168
00:10:35,405 --> 00:10:38,184
I might as well study until dawn.

169
00:10:38,891 --> 00:10:40,577
Watching for cars, okay?

170
00:10:40,628 --> 00:10:41,504
Okay

171
00:10:53,238 --> 00:10:56,046
Yan... Huh? He's dozing off?

172
00:11:00,079 --> 00:11:01,643
Kenichi, Kenichi!

173
00:11:01,693 --> 00:11:03,188
Hey, you can't be snoozing

174
00:11:03,239 --> 00:11:05,824
Seize the moment, wake up quickly!

175
00:11:11,340 --> 00:11:12,640
Oh, this is bad

176
00:11:15,276 --> 00:11:16,720
Finally woke him up

177
00:11:23,494 --> 00:11:26,014
Kenichi's results are really unexpected

178
00:11:28,907 --> 00:11:30,584
Finally success!

179
00:11:35,567 --> 00:11:37,720
Congratulations, Kenichi, you did very well

180
00:11:39,953 --> 00:11:41,784
Kenichi, congratulations

181
00:11:43,372 --> 00:11:45,304
Here, this is your prize

182
00:11:46,045 --> 00:11:48,434
How can I accept such a big prize?

183
00:11:48,475 --> 00:11:49,325
Huh, what are
you saying?

184
00:11:49,365 --> 00:11:51,369
It was hard work to get Kenichi good results

185
00:11:51,419 --> 00:11:52,793
Kenichi, here, this is yours

186
00:11:52,844 --> 00:11:53,813
So small?

187
00:11:53,864 --> 00:11:55,870
Alright, we can eat now.

188
00:11:56,497 --> 00:11:57,933
Ah, Hattori-kun, you got off well

189
00:11:57,984 --> 00:12:00,949
- Such a big prize?
- Kenichi, why don't we trade?

190
00:12:01,000 --> 00:12:02,964
Oh my, you'd really trade with me?

191
00:12:07,474 --> 00:12:10,264
An encyclopedia...

192
00:12:10,587 --> 00:12:13,147
So it's a quartz watch? That's great.

193
00:12:17,920 --> 00:12:19,106
Mom is really smart.

194
00:12:19,157 --> 00:12:20,464
Kenichi fell for it

195
00:12:21,031 --> 00:12:23,224
Yan...

196
00:12:26,396 --> 00:12:29,210
［Yours Truly, Cooking Expert］

197
00:12:34,607 --> 00:12:36,617
Ah, Mommy, just rest a bit.

198
00:12:36,667 --> 00:12:39,744
Today, the two of us will cook for you.

199
00:12:39,800 --> 00:12:40,420
Go rest.

200
00:12:40,465 --> 00:12:41,563
What are you talking about?

201
00:12:41,614 --> 00:12:43,581
Today isn't Mother's Day or Father's Day.

202
00:12:43,622 --> 00:12:46,263
Why are you doing this?

203
00:12:46,314 --> 00:12:47,784
You usually work hard.

204
00:12:47,834 --> 00:12:50,017
Today we want to repay you.

205
00:12:50,067 --> 00:12:51,573
Is it really to repay me?

206
00:12:51,624 --> 00:12:54,600
Okay, Mom, don't say anymore, go...

207
00:12:54,846 --> 00:12:56,960
Why don't you just sit here and rest first?

208
00:12:58,901 --> 00:13:01,880
Fortunately, Mom didn't notice or think much of it.

209
00:13:02,521 --> 00:13:04,213
If we perform well this time,

210
00:13:04,271 --> 00:13:05,358
next month we can ask her

211
00:13:05,408 --> 00:13:06,859
to give us more pocket money.

212
00:13:06,900 --> 00:13:07,761
Yan...

213
00:13:07,894 --> 00:13:10,392
Be careful, cut slowly.

214
00:13:10,447 --> 00:13:11,525
Is this how you cut it?

215
00:13:11,575 --> 00:13:12,592
It won't be ready until morning.

216
00:13:12,616 --> 00:13:14,625
Here, throw it to me then!

217
00:13:14,676 --> 00:13:16,368
What? Throw the ingredients to you?

218
00:13:17,214 --> 00:13:19,431
Come, let me demonstrate!

219
00:13:21,827 --> 00:13:23,584
Ah, I get it now

220
00:13:23,635 --> 00:13:24,780
For Hattori-Kun

221
00:13:24,807 --> 00:13:26,544
- it's a piece of cake. Here it comes!
- Yan!

222
00:13:29,664 --> 00:13:31,027
Amazing!

223
00:13:31,879 --> 00:13:33,541
Wow, amazing!

224
00:13:33,592 --> 00:13:35,374
This move is called "Radish Quick Knife Chop!"

225
00:13:35,424 --> 00:13:37,049
Ah, you're really something

226
00:13:37,104 --> 00:13:37,919
Alright then!

227
00:13:38,464 --> 00:13:40,108
Time to chop vegetables, catch this!

228
00:13:40,159 --> 00:13:42,104
My sword skills are all-powerful.

229
00:13:47,020 --> 00:13:47,964
Chop onions!

230
00:13:50,584 --> 00:13:51,611
Radishes!

231
00:13:52,184 --> 00:13:53,311
Here it comes...

232
00:13:54,053 --> 00:13:56,100
Next off, we're chopping pork

233
00:14:00,040 --> 00:14:03,303
Spam! Oh, there's still... oh my.

234
00:14:03,354 --> 00:14:05,663
Hey, chop this! Here, vermicelli.

235
00:14:08,809 --> 00:14:11,456
The vermicelli is too soft, can't cut it.

236
00:14:11,697 --> 00:14:13,358
Oh no, it's all cut up now.

237
00:14:13,409 --> 00:14:15,452
Why are we cooking so much?

238
00:14:16,350 --> 00:14:17,445
Give me more!

239
00:14:17,977 --> 00:14:20,104
Let me eat more...

240
00:14:23,854 --> 00:14:25,705
Oh, what's going on?

241
00:14:27,852 --> 00:14:30,767
Oh, is Kenichi's family planning a party?

242
00:14:31,220 --> 00:14:33,793
Oh, right, what kind of party is it?

243
00:14:34,104 --> 00:14:36,304
Could it be Kenichi's birthday?

244
00:14:36,354 --> 00:14:39,156
Or is it Hattori-kun's birthday, so...

245
00:14:39,207 --> 00:14:40,298
Oh, I get it.

246
00:14:40,348 --> 00:14:42,544
It must be Shishimaru's welcome party!

247
00:14:43,567 --> 00:14:45,312
Really? Then I'll join too.

248
00:14:45,362 --> 00:14:47,702
- I'm going too!
- I might as well go.

249
00:14:51,547 --> 00:14:54,287
Oh, why cook so many dishes?

250
00:14:54,947 --> 00:14:56,138
Hey, don't ask so many questions.

251
00:14:56,188 --> 00:14:57,636
Hurry up and sit down first.

252
00:14:57,687 --> 00:14:59,101
Oh, what day is it today?

253
00:14:59,152 --> 00:15:00,141
Why make so many dishes?

254
00:15:00,688 --> 00:15:03,758
I heard Kenichi and Hattori-kun worked together to make them.

255
00:15:03,808 --> 00:15:05,624
- Good evening
- Good evening

256
00:15:06,670 --> 00:15:08,084
Who are you guys?

257
00:15:08,134 --> 00:15:10,682
Thank you so much for inviting us to attend

258
00:15:10,733 --> 00:15:12,954
What? You're saying I invited you to a party?

259
00:15:14,300 --> 00:15:17,424
Today, um... isn't it Shishimaru's welcome party?

260
00:15:18,067 --> 00:15:18,777
No

261
00:15:18,828 --> 00:15:21,669
Today is my dad and mom's wedding anniversary

262
00:15:22,773 --> 00:15:24,368
Oh dear, I really forgot

263
00:15:24,419 --> 00:15:27,632
-Today is a big day!
-I completely forgot too!

264
00:15:27,683 --> 00:15:28,689
Shishimaru

265
00:15:28,739 --> 00:15:30,089
It's not a party for you at all

266
00:15:30,140 --> 00:15:32,526
Why are you just making things up?

267
00:15:33,746 --> 00:15:34,992
I'm very sorry.

268
00:15:35,532 --> 00:15:38,245
But it doesn't matter, everyone, please come in and sit down.

269
00:15:38,295 --> 00:15:39,881
Please go in, go ahead.

270
00:15:40,097 --> 00:15:40,988
That's right.

271
00:15:41,039 --> 00:15:43,285
Since we've prepared so much food anyway

272
00:15:43,335 --> 00:15:45,401
Please everyone, come and eat.

273
00:15:45,848 --> 00:15:49,128
- Uncle and Auntie, congratulations!
- Uncle and Auntie, congratulations!

274
00:15:49,267 --> 00:15:51,006
Thank you so much, thank you all!

275
00:15:51,056 --> 00:15:54,134
Kenichi and Hattori-Kun, it's so rare to see you so enthusiastic.

276
00:15:54,185 --> 00:15:56,219
It's nothing, but I have a small request.

277
00:15:56,270 --> 00:15:59,386
We'd like you to increase our allowance next season.

278
00:15:59,437 --> 00:16:02,184
You two really have a complete plan.

279
00:16:02,863 --> 00:16:04,674
How could we possibly refuse?

280
00:16:04,699 --> 00:16:05,984
That's right, let's agree to it.

281
00:16:07,090 --> 00:16:10,264
- Our strategy is a success! Time to eat!
- We won!

282
00:16:10,784 --> 00:16:12,643
- Let's eat!
- Let's eat!

283
00:16:14,336 --> 00:16:15,755
Hey, hurry up and eat.

284
00:16:15,814 --> 00:16:19,354
- Wow, if he eats that fast, he'll finish it all!
- He ate it all!

285
00:16:27,980 --> 00:16:30,064
Wow, he'll finish it all so easily.

286
00:16:30,105 --> 00:16:31,276
So fast?

287
00:16:34,069 --> 00:16:36,482
Shishimaru, how can you be so lazy after eating?

288
00:16:36,532 --> 00:16:37,791
Hurry up and help with the chores.

289
00:16:37,862 --> 00:16:39,254
Don't be a gluttonous lazybones!

290
00:16:40,957 --> 00:16:42,588
Hey, Mommy,
hurry up and rest.

291
00:16:42,628 --> 00:16:44,638
Let us finish the leftovers, you go to bed.

292
00:16:44,689 --> 00:16:46,548
Okay, thanks for your help.

293
00:16:46,824 --> 00:16:48,624
Yan...

294
00:16:48,779 --> 00:16:50,804
So many dishes to wash, how long will it take?

295
00:16:50,855 --> 00:16:53,589
Don't worry, we had to do the cooking.

296
00:16:53,639 --> 00:16:55,689
So Shishimaru is responsible for washing the dishes.

297
00:16:56,105 --> 00:16:57,480
What? W... what?

298
00:16:57,505 --> 00:16:59,959
Woah, that's right, Shishimaru didn't do anything at all

299
00:17:00,010 --> 00:17:02,373
You ate so much, it's only fair you wash the dishes

300
00:17:02,424 --> 00:17:03,704
Yan...

301
00:17:34,160 --> 00:17:37,224
Ah, Shishimaru is actually quite good at washing dishes

302
00:17:40,714 --> 00:17:43,727
Actually, when Shishimaru does work, he's really very capable

303
00:17:51,804 --> 00:17:54,929
Oh no, this is bad, how did this happen?

304
00:17:55,757 --> 00:17:58,959
Your help celebrating my wedding anniversary made me very happy

305
00:17:59,009 --> 00:18:01,673
But... this is really too disappointing

306
00:18:01,723 --> 00:18:04,052
Kenichi, you must compensate all the smashed dishes

307
00:18:04,093 --> 00:18:05,713
Next month, I'll deduct it from your allowance

308
00:18:05,754 --> 00:18:07,333
That's only fair

309
00:18:08,173 --> 00:18:11,069
- Hurry up and clean up!
- Oh no, this is miserable!

310
00:18:11,126 --> 00:18:13,084
Shishimaru, you're the one who got us into this

311
00:18:13,135 --> 00:18:14,325
It's all your fault

312
00:18:14,585 --> 00:18:15,750
I'm sorry

313
00:18:15,801 --> 00:18:17,257
We were supposed to have more pocket money

314
00:18:17,297 --> 00:18:19,024
But it backfired

